p>           <li><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Research:</b>             Above all else, comedy must be accurate. As part of our covert ops             force, interns research upcoming victims of our mockery. Prerequisite:             Comfort with such research tools as dictionaries, search engines and             your friend who never misses Dawson's. </font>             <p>           <li><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Editorial             Administration:</b> Despite the advances in digital storage and communications,             we do need interns to help us file and communicate with other humans.             Prerequisite: Comfort with manila folders, the Outlook Express e-mail             client and the touch-tone telephone. </font>         </ul>        <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br>          Editorial interns work on-site in our luxurious offices in Brooklyn,           New York.</font></p>        <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Your dreams           are waiting. Are you ready? </font> </p>        <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Contact           <a href="MAILTO:working@modernhumorist.com"> <b>working@modernhumorist.com</b></a>           for more information. </font>        <p align="center"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><img src="../images/banana.gif" width="24" height="22">           <br>          </font></p>      </td>					</tr>					<tr>						<td></td>					</tr>					<tr>						<td></td>					</tr>				</table>			</center>		</body>	</html>	<!-- #EndLibraryItem -->	</p>